# Method
Key Resources


What are the steps to solve the problem
1. Define

2. Importing
Key activities
- Import the data
- Describe the Data
- Describe the columns
- Describe the distribution
- Uniform | Normal | Exponential



3. Massaging
Key activities
- Remove NAS
- Replace Special Characters
- Rename columns


4. Descriptive
## Numerical variables
 Proof of Normality:
- Inspect Histogram and normal quantile plot
- Inspect Values of Skewness & Kurtosis

## Categorical variables
- Frequency Count
- Test for association


5. Predictive

Sampling
- Simple Random Sample (SRS)
- Systematic Sampling (follows pattern like every 10th item)
- Stratified Sampling (divide into characteristics like male or female)
